      "author": "ocapraro",
      "description": "## What's Changed\r\nChanged grouping for super and sub scripts which was messing up integrals. To see this change in full effect remove the following shortcuts from settings:\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"op\":\"^\",\r\n  \"format\":\"{{%s1%}^{%s2%}}\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"op\":\"_\",\r\n  \"format\":\"{{%s1%}_{%s2%}}\"\r\n},\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/ocapraro/obsidian-math-plus/compare/0.5.1...0.6.0",
